p;long-term project&nbsp;to prevent unwanted pregnancies,&nbsp;STDs, and to reduce domestic violence.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/personal-development-desarrollo-personal/\">See more...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un proyecto a largo plazo para prevenir los embarazos no deseados, las ETS y reducir la violencia doméstica.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/personal-development-desarrollo-personal/\">Ver más...</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"20px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#b0884b\"}}} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide has-text-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-background\" style=\"background-color:#b0884b;color:#b0884b\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#bdbd14\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#bdbd14\">Accomplished Projects /&nbsp;Proyectos Realizados</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                FUNDACION PARA EL PROGRESO -&nbsp;<a href=\"http://fundacion-avanzar.jimdo.com/programs/accomplished-projects/fundepro/\">FUNDEPRO</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Single Mothers\' Home / Hogar para Madres Solteras -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/single-mothers-home/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Pasta Fabric / Fabrica de Fideos -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/sewing-costume-atelier-second-hand-shop/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Sewing &nbsp;Atelier &amp; Second Hand Shop / Taller de costura y tienda de segunda mano - &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/sewing-costume-atelier-second-hand-shop/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Bakery / Panaderia \"San José de Calasanz\" -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/bakery-san-jos%C3%A9-de-calasanz/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Day Care and Kindergarten /&nbsp;Guardería y jardín de infantes \"José Hidalgo\" -&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/day-care-und-kindergarten/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Humanitarian Foundation / Fundación Humanitaria \" Sonrisas con Amor\"&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/sewing-costume-atelier-second-hand-shop/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">                                Mural Pediatric Unit / Mural de la Unidad Pediátrica&nbsp;-&nbsp;Hospital \"Vincente Corral Moscoso\" Cuenca, Ecuador&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.fundacion-avanzar.com/programs-programas/accomplished-projects-proyectos-realizados/1000-foot-mural/\">See more / Ver más</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'porfolio', '', '', '2023-06-29 10:00:22', '2023-06-29 15:00:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=32', 0, 'page', '', 0);
