(211, 1, '2023-06-26 22:01:08', '2023-06-27 03:01:08', '<!-- wp:cover {\"overlayColor\":\"nv-site-bg\",\"minHeight\":50,\"minHeightUnit\":\"px\",\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:50px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"overlayColor\":\"nv-light-bg\",\"minHeight\":600,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover aligncenter\" style=\"min-height:600px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-nv-light-bg-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"0px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:0px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#e9e6a5\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Our Mission</mark></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Fundación Avanzar seeks to align itself with the mission pursued by UN Women, which is to promote gender equality and empower women to accelerate progress toward improving the conditions of their lives. Investing in women’s economic empowerment sets a direct path towards gender equality, poverty eradication, and inclusive economic growth.<br></mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">To this end, Fundación Avanzar has implemented a numbers of initiatives which support Social Economy Enterprises formed by women, also called \"Female Economy Enterprises\", concentrating on the aspects in which they have most room for improvement: Training within their particular areas of work, on the one hand, and handling business models, on the other hand – both of which are fundamental to increasing the leadership and successful participation of women within the family economy.</mark><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Avanzar offers the female participants support in a variety of formats such as chats, coaching sessions, and mentoring. In addition to university courses, online tools like Zoom or Facebook Live have proven to be extremely valuable communication tools.  chats, sesiones de coaching y mentoring. </mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-text-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-neve-text-color-color has-text-color\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#e9e6a5\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Nuestra Misión</mark></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">La Fundación Avanzar busca alinearse con la misión que persigue ONU Mujeres, que es promover la igualdad de género y empoderar a las mujeres para acelerar el progreso hacia la mejora de sus condiciones de vida. Invertir en el empoderamiento económico de las mujeres marca un camino directo hacia la igualdad de género, la erradicación de la pobreza y el crecimiento económico inclusivo.<br></mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Con este fin, la Fundación Avanzar ha puesto en marcha una serie de iniciativas que apoyan a las Empresas de Economía Social formadas por mujeres, también llamadas \"Empresas de Economía Femenina\", centrándose en los aspectos en los que tienen más margen de mejora: Por un lado, la formación en sus áreas de trabajo y, por otro, el manejo de modelos de negocio, aspectos ambos fundamentales para incrementar el liderazgo y la participación exitosa de las mujeres en la economía familiar.</mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Avanzar ofrece a las participantes apoyo en diversos formatos, como chats, sesiones de coaching y mentoring. Además de los cursos universitarios, herramientas en línea como Zoom o Facebook Live han demostrado ser instrumentos de comunicación muy valiosos.</mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"40px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"overlayColor\":\"nv-dark-bg\",\"minHeight\":600,\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:600px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-nv-dark-bg-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"0px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:0px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"nv-text-dark-bg\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-nv-text-dark-bg-color has-text-color\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#e9e6a5\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Our Vision</mark></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"nv-text-dark-bg\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-nv-text-dark-bg-color has-text-color\">The program we offer&nbsp;provide&nbsp;their beneficiaries with the opportunity, the knowledge, and the resources to create for themselves a productive and prosperous life, complete with self-determination, dignity, responsibility, and freedom. We are a dynamic, innovative, and efficient non-profit organization&nbsp;generating&nbsp;concrete contributions to under-privileged women and their families.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"20px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"0px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:0px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#e9e6a5\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Nuestra Visión</mark></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Los programas que ofrecemos proporcionan a sus beneficiarias la oportunidad, los conocimientos y los recursos para crear por sí mismas una vida productiva y próspera, plena de autodeterminación, dignidad, responsabilidad y libertad. Somos una organización sin ánimo de lucro dinámica, innovadora y eficiente que genera contribuciones concretas para las mujeres desfavorecidas y sus familias.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"40px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"overlayColor\":\"nv-site-bg\",\"minHeight\":420,\"align\":\"full\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:420px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-nv-site-bg-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"14px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:14px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"className\":\"ticss-f6fc7494\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column ticss-f6fc7494\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"24px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"neve-text-color\",\"className\":\"has-text-align-center\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-text-align-center has-neve-text-color-color has-text-color\">Our Strategic Plan</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Work in a competent way, specialized and efficient to respond to and grow with the demands of society.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Identify and define new projects which address the socio-economic demands that are neglected by the governmental and private sectors; support existing projects with great potential for development and strength.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Create relationships with other organizations in order to support each other and enrich each other‘s work.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Offer our collaborators the opportunity to work independently to produce and grow.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Welcome volunteers who help us with their knowledge and work.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Maintain a small, transparent administration with low expenses with the purpose of dedicating the majority of our funding to complete our mission.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"20px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"className\":\"ticss-a5b4df29\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column ticss-a5b4df29\"><!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"24px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3,\"textColor\":\"neve-text-color\",\"className\":\"has-text-align-center\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-text-align-center has-neve-text-color-color has-text-color\">Nuestro Plan Estratégico</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Trabajar de forma competente, especializada y eficiente para responder y crecer con las demandas de la sociedad.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Identificar y definir nuevos proyectos que atiendan las demandas socioeconómicas desatendidas por los sectores gubernamental y privado; apoyar proyectos existentes con gran potencial de desarrollo y fortaleza.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Crear relaciones con otras organizaciones para apoyarnos mutuamente y enriquecer nuestro trabajo.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Ofrecer a nuestros colaboradores la oportunidad de trabajar de forma independiente para producir y crecer.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Acoger a voluntarios que nos ayuden con sus conocimientos y su trabajo.</mark></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-nv-dark-bg-color\">Mantener una administración pequeña, transparente y con pocos gastos con el fin de dedicar la mayor parte de nuestra finan